column5: Had a small 11 boat tourney on Six Mile yesterday, despite the high of 8 degrees and 25km winds, my good friend and I managed to win the tourney with 19.50 lbs and big fish at 5.58  Report to follow...
MMMMMMMM, Bass porn. Nice job out there. Congrats on the tourny win!!! Pig n Jig ? jerk b8 ?
Nice pics...  Nice win....  What do you do with the fish after the awards are presented?
19.50 out of six mile is excellent.  Congrats, nice bag.  I really like that lake.
Well done. 6 Mile can really produce at times if you can avoid the heavy boat traffic.
NICE Steve!!!  Congrats on the win Leechman
Looks like a fun day on the 6.  Always a fun lake to fish.  Congrets on the win.  What was the grand prize??
